# User Stories – WebFood

## Customer

As a customer, I want to browse the food menu so I can see what dishes are available.

As a customer, I want to see the details of a food item so I know its price and description.

As a customer, I want to add food items to my cart so I can order them later.

As a customer, I want to log in to my account so I can manage my orders.

As a customer, I want to contact the website so I can ask questions or send feedback.

## Admin

As an admin, I want to manage food products so I can update the menu when needed.
